question: 21 + Joonie
answer:
PROMPT: “We’re in the middle of a thunderstorm and you wanna stop and feel the rain?”

- 

You were stood outside of a restaurant dressed in a dress and heels, ready to make a beeline straight to your apartment just down the street, when your boyfriend suggested taking a slow stroll to ‘feel the rain’. 

“Are you fucking serious?” you yell over the loud noise of the rain hitting the pavement and the buildings surrounding you.

“What? It’s relaxing!” he shrugged and defended himself. 

“We’re in the middle of a thunderstorm and you wanna stop and feel the rain?” you questioned further, not understanding why he didn’t want to run back to the warmth and comfort of your apartment. 

“But we could recreate one of those romantic kissing scenes in the rain. You know, the one in all of the cringey movies” he tried to reason, coming closer and placing his hands on your waist and flashing his dimples at you. 

You chuckled. How could he call those movies cringy but seem so desperate about recreating scenes from them. “You’re gross” you spoke while hitting the end of his nose with your finger.

“But”, you smiled, “I’d like that”.

summary: BTS Falling For A Fuckgirl Ask: bts falling in love with a fuckgirl? 👅 Update: KS has been dead inside taking a bunch of house...
body:
BTS Falling For A Fuckgirl

Ask: bts falling in love with a fuckgirl? 👅

Update: KS has been dead inside taking a bunch of house sitting jobs and is currently at her second job listening to the rainfall outside peacefully. (I fuggin love the rainnn)

Namjoon

Would come at this in a cautious manner. Yes, he likes you, but he won’t do crap if those feelings aren’t matched. He’s going to be upfront about his feelings and expect you to do the same.

“Fuck these games. If you’re not mine, I’m not yours.”

Yoongi

Tries to act aloof and carefree. He won’t like that he has these feelings for you but he simply can’t stop himself.

“Shit, here we go again.”

Jin

He’s worldwide handsome, get on his level! He’d be a tad worried that this girl was just playing with him but would reciprocate as much as she did to not seem desperate.

“Wow, such wifey material!”

“Jin, I’m not your wifey.”

“…Yet.”

Hoseok

Would try and meet you halfway but will be completely lost on how to woo you. He’s hella into you, and he’ll show it outright, but he won’t actively pursue you unless you show you want him.

“You’re absolutely beautiful and deserve the world. I’ll wait until you’re ready for me to give it to you.”

Taehyung

Would match your fuckgirl to his fuckboi. Don’t test him. Yes, you’re a badass, but that doesn’t mean he can’t measure up either.

“We’ll see who wins this little stand-off.”

Jimin

Lost af. Admires your independence but is also slightly intimidated. He wants you, it’s easy to see, but he’ll be worried about opening himself up to you.

“I’m in this until it’s too late.”

Jungkook

Constantly questions himself on his feelings. Why you? Why him? Why anything?

“Why am I in love alone?” (If y’all get this reference, I love you)

-KS

| Masterlist |

body:
Namjoon 「he hits you during an argument」

Here you go, love🤧🤧💞 i tried to make it less painful:(( i hope you like it💓

might be triggering for some

You have just stepped in the dorm when you heard a very familiar shouting from the practice room. Namjoon and you were not in a good term. You have quite an argument with him yesterday over a very stupid subject. Him, not eating healthy enough these days. He raised his voice in the middle of the argument and you decided to leave before you replied him with an even louder voice.

You know yesterday’s conversation won’t go anywhere right, so you come to the dorm today to apologize, not knowing what you did wrong actually. But you hate it when you don’t talk to him.

You open the practice room’s door slowly, still hearing loud shouting voices. Now, not only from Namjoon but also Yoongi and Hoseok.

“You are going to get it right, Namjoon!” Hoseok’s voice echoed in the big practice room.

“How? How the fuck am I going to get it right? I tried like thousands of time already. It just doesn’t make sense.”

“Your mind is not in the right place now. Get a rest.” Yoongi said while walking away from him to grab a bottle of water. He throws the water bottle to Namjoon and he catches it perfectly.

“I am okay. We can continue.”

“Namjoon, listen to Yoongi.” Seokjin advised.

“I said I’m okay, hyung!”

You sighed in the corner of the room. The group is too tired to notice your presence.

“Get a rest, Kim Namjoon. I’m not going to repeat myself.”

“Please rest, Namjoon hyung. We still get a lot of time to ace this choreography,” the youngest opened his mouth.

“Not you too, Jungkook.”

“Get a rest, Namjoon,” you said. All of their attentions are shifted to you. “You are pushing yourself too hard. You need to know when to stop.” Namjoon walked towards you. He does not seem very happy with your sudden remark. You know Namjoon for a long time, never once have you seen him like this.

“Why are you here?”

“Am I not allowed to be here?” you asked him back.

“I thought you are the one leaving yesterday. Now you came back like nothing happened?”

“You are putting the blame on me?”

“It’s open to interpretation.” Namjoon walked back to the group after replying to your question. You could feel your heart beating faster and your muscle tensing up.

“Kim Namjoon.”

“I came here to make sure you are alive and you are okay because you can’t seem to take care of yourself, and you are making me dead worried. Understand?”

You really come for a peace mission, but how he treated you was nothing close to that. Namjoon turned and walked back to you. The room was quiet, maybe the other boys are too scared to make any noises.

“I didn’t ask for that.”

“It’s common sense.”

“What common sense come with treating me like a child?”

“It is because I am worried about you, dumbass!”

“If you could take care of yourself better, maybe I don’t need to-“

That’s the end of your sentence. Before you knew it, his palm is now on your cheek, leaving behind a stinging pain. You shake your head a little, both for Namjoon, and Seokjin, who you see is walking towards you.

You picked your bag up from the floor and leave before Namjoon could even say anthing.

“Y/n! Fuck. Y/n!” Namjoon chases you to the front door, trying to stop you from leaving.

“Y/n, wait. I’m so sorry, I don’t know what happen to me. I didn’t- fuck I didn’t mean that.” He tried to reach out for your red cheek before you slapped his hand.

“Don’t you dare touch me.”

“Y/n, please.” You could already see tears cornering his eyes, threatening to fall.

“Don’t fucking touch me!”

“Y/n please, don’t leave. I’m sorry.”

You slammed the door behind you and ran back to your apartment. Your walking pace becomes slower as the tears try to heal the pain from your cheek.

And for the first time, you feel fear towards him.

“I came here to make sure you are alive and you are okay because you can’t seem to take care of yourself, and you are making me dead worried. Understand?”

You really come for a peace mission, but how he treated you was nothing close to that. Namjoon turned and walked back to you. The room was quiet, maybe the other boys are too scared to make any noises.

“I didn’t ask for that.”

“It’s common sense.”

“What common sense come with treating me like a child?”

“It is because I am worried about you, dumbass!”

“If you could take care of yourself better, maybe I don’t need to-“

That’s the end of your sentence. Before you knew it, his palm is now on your cheek, leaving behind a stinging pain. You shake your head a little, both for Namjoon, and Seokjin, who you see is walking towards you.

You picked your bag up from the floor and leave before Namjoon could even say anthing.

“Y/n! Fuck. Y/n!” Namjoon chases you to the front door, trying to stop you from leaving.

“Y/n, wait. I’m so sorry, I don’t know what happen to me. I didn’t- fuck I didn’t mean that.” He tried to reach out for your red cheek before you slapped his hand.

“Don’t you dare touch me.”

“Y/n, please.” You could already see tears cornering his eyes, threatening to fall.

“Don’t fucking touch me!”

“Y/n please, don’t leave. I’m sorry.”

You slammed the door behind you and ran back to your apartment. Your walking pace becomes slower as the tears try to heal the pain from your cheek.

And for the first time, you feel fear towards him.
